data.value:
The following are the features that available in the version.
V 2.0.031022 (Major Chage) - Combine interface of form 1 to form 2. - Make easy acess to the configuration page - Remove configuration button V 1.3.0 (Major Change) - Network configuration page user interface update
V 1.2.1 (Change) - Add more selection when selecting network type - Change WiFi command
V 1.1.0 (Change) - Remove a few parts and added a few button to test the sensors connected
V 1.0.4 (Fix) - Fix HEX number reading
V 1.0.3 (Added) - Refresh button to check the COM Ports availability
V 1.0.1 (Added) - Save port connection settings button is added to ease the connection for next time. -Three input sensors and the network type can be reset by using configuration page after connected to the serial port.
V 1.0.0 - Serial port connection configuration setting including serial communication baud rate, data bits, stop bits and parity. - Main page are displayed with connected device number, connected sensors, EEPROM memory usage, connection status, type of network, and status of network module. - Three input sensors and the network type can be configure by using configuration page after connected to the serial port. - Sensor and network type configuration will call system command to the device, the device should receive the command and perform specific tasks such as write, read and save configurations from the memory.
